text: Dušan Vičík (born 18 December 1960) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Olomouc
